        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Plans for campaign, and need of reinforcements</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Camp Salado </placeName><date when="1835-10-26">Oct. 26 1835</date></p>

<p>I shall move with the <persName>Army </persName>today to the <placeName>Missions</placeName>, and press the 
operations as fast as my force will permit&#8212; I have but four hundred effective
<persName>men</persName>&#8212; <persName>Genl. Cos</persName> has about 800 or 900, and is well fortified</p>

<p>We need <persName>reinforcements</persName>, I shall persevere here&#8212; My health is very
bad&#8212; There has been skirmishing dayly but no loss on our side&#8212;</p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName> [Rubric]</p>

<p>The <persName>members of the convention</persName> except the <persName>comr </persName>and his <persName>staff </persName>leave here
today to hold the convention on the <date when="1835-11-01">1 Novr</date> or as soon as they get a
<persName>quorum</persName>.</p>

<p><persName>S. F. Austin</persName></p>
<p>To the <persName>Committee </persName><placeName>San Felipe</placeName></p>


        </div1>
